00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:34,719
[SPEAKER_02] nego je rekao i tu mi se kod njega dopada,

677
00:36:34,719 --> 00:36:35,059
[SPEAKER_02] nije sve to glumi.

678
00:36:35,059 --> 00:36:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] O to ste dobro rekli,

679
00:36:36,139 --> 00:36:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] preko interneta se potpuno mijenja medijska slika

680
00:36:39,179 --> 00:36:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] i imam dojam da je politička korektnost

681
00:36:41,719 --> 00:36:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] nikad u gorem položaju nije bila.

682
00:36:45,079 --> 00:36:48,780
[SPEAKER_00] Danas se sve više ljudi usudi reći ono što misli,

683
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer dosadlo im je to hipermoraliziranje

684
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] koje ste često su menili.

685
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

686
00:36:54,039 --> 00:36:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo tu u podređenom položu

687
00:36:55,719 --> 00:36:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] u Europskoj uniji

688
00:36:56,559 --> 00:36:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je to i dalje zakonski jako regulirano.

689
00:36:58,739 --> 00:37:00,239
[SPEAKER_00] Nemamo sve te amandmane.

690
00:37:00,239 --> 00:37:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da pače, drago mi,

691
00:37:01,559 --> 00:37:02,599
[SPEAKER_02] ja prosto ne zaboravim,

692
00:37:02,599 --> 00:37:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] baš taj moraliziranje,

693
00:37:03,559 --> 00:37:05,559
[SPEAKER_02] hipermoraliziranje,

694
00:37:05,559 --> 00:37:08,559
[SPEAKER_02] pa krasna slika od Armina Molle,

695
00:37:08,559 --> 00:37:09,380
[SPEAKER_02] Armin Molle,

696
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:10,480
[SPEAKER_02] sjeti ću se mi,

697
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,360
[SPEAKER_02] ja prosto te sjeti,

698
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:13,260
[SPEAKER_02] poznati bi joj prijatelj Karla Šmita,

699
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:14,699
[SPEAKER_02] antropolog njemački.

700
00:37:14,699 --> 00:37:15,739
[SPEAKER_02] Gelen,

701
00:37:15,739 --> 00:37:17,000
[SPEAKER_02] Arnold Gelen,

702
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:18,420
[SPEAKER_02] on je hipermoralizmus,

703
00:37:18,420 --> 00:37:19,440
[SPEAKER_02] napisao je knjigu,

704
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:21,460
[SPEAKER_02] to bi trebali studenti čitati,

705
00:37:21,460 --> 00:37:23,139
[SPEAKER_02] on je jako dobro skužio američku,

706
00:37:23,139 --> 00:37:24,099
[SPEAKER_02] shvatio,

707
00:37:24,099 --> 00:37:26,260
[SPEAKER_02] detektirao američku psihologiju,

708
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:26,940
[SPEAKER_02] Arnold Gelen,

709
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:27,900
[SPEAKER_02] moralizmus,

710
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:29,039
[SPEAKER_02] on hipermoralizmus,

711
00:37:29,039 --> 00:37:31,019
[SPEAKER_02] moralizam i hipermoralizam,

712
00:37:31,019 --> 00:37:32,380
[SPEAKER_02] gdje on, kaže,

713
00:37:32,380 --> 00:37:33,300
[SPEAKER_02] odmah nakon rata je

714
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:35,460
[SPEAKER_02] napisao to knjigu,

715
00:37:36,260 --> 00:37:37,539
[SPEAKER_02] kako sve to dolazi

716
00:37:37,539 --> 00:37:38,960
[SPEAKER_02] iz tega američkog,

717
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,059
[SPEAKER_02] Amerika je okupirala

718
00:37:40,059 --> 00:37:41,079
[SPEAKER_02] nakon Rosijskog rata,

719
00:37:41,079 --> 00:37:41,920
[SPEAKER_02] ne samo u Njemačku,

720
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,820
[SPEAKER_02] nego u cijelu Evropu,

721
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] najme za stranaj,

722
00:37:43,559 --> 00:37:44,639
[SPEAKER_02] i školstvo,

723
00:37:44,639 --> 00:37:45,480
[SPEAKER_02] i jedno i drugo,

724
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:47,480
[SPEAKER_02] i sva ta politička korektnost,

725
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:49,000
[SPEAKER_02] akademska samocenzura,

726
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,000
[SPEAKER_02] koju danas vidite,

727
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,760
[SPEAKER_02] pogotovo u Zapadnoj Evropi,

728
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:53,039
[SPEAKER_02] pogotovo u Njemačkoj,

729
00:37:53,039 --> 00:37:54,579
[SPEAKER_02] gdje ima patološke proporcije,

730
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:56,440
[SPEAKER_02] a sve više i više kod nas,

731
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:58,340
[SPEAKER_02] ne samo kod naših političara,

732
00:37:58,340 --> 00:37:59,980
[SPEAKER_02] nego i na prisadju,

733
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:01,360
[SPEAKER_02] i na filozofskom fakultetu,

734
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:01,860
[SPEAKER_02] i s uglje,

735
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:03,780
[SPEAKER_02] sve se više i više osjeća.

736
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:05,599
[SPEAKER_02] To je jedno moraliziranje,

737
00:38:05,599 --> 00:38:06,440
[SPEAKER_02] ja ću to nazvati,

738
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:07,460
[SPEAKER_02] već sam o tom govorio,

739
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:09,860
[SPEAKER_02] samo kastrirajući jedan diskurs,

740
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:10,619
[SPEAKER_02] zašto?

741
00:38:10,619 --> 00:38:12,079
[SPEAKER_02] Ljudi se boje za svoje,

742
00:38:12,079 --> 00:38:15,079
[SPEAKER_02] ne samo fizički za onu stvar,

743
00:38:15,079 --> 00:38:18,539
[SPEAKER_02] nego se boje za svoje sine kure,

744
00:38:18,539 --> 00:38:19,300
[SPEAKER_02] za uglje, da.

745
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:21,239
[SPEAKER_02] To mogli s prve ruke dati imene,

746
00:38:21,239 --> 00:38:22,960
[SPEAKER_02] bezmo na to neću sad govoriti,

747
00:38:23,559 --> 00:38:25,739
[SPEAKER_02] ali taj jedan hipermoralistički stav

748
00:38:25,739 --> 00:38:26,659
[SPEAKER_02] nam jako šteti.

749
00:38:26,659 --> 00:38:28,219
[SPEAKER_02] Da se čovjek pita,

750
00:38:28,219 --> 00:38:29,179
[SPEAKER_02] što mi je onda bolje,

751
00:38:29,179 --> 00:38:30,559
[SPEAKER_02] onaj komunistički pendrik,

752
00:38:30,559 --> 00:38:34,179
[SPEAKER_02] gdje mi dođe neki pandur sa pendrikom,

753
00:38:34,179 --> 00:38:35,059
[SPEAKER_02] znam da je divljak,

754
00:38:35,059 --> 00:38:36,440
[SPEAKER_02] joj ga mogu odmah prepoznati,

755
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:39,760
[SPEAKER_02] nego neki dušobrižnik,

756
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,099
[SPEAKER_02] koji će mi moralizirati

757
00:38:41,099 --> 00:38:42,280
[SPEAKER_02] iz neki USA-da,

758
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,460
[SPEAKER_02] ili iz bivše američke ambasade,

759
00:38:44,460 --> 00:38:45,920
[SPEAKER_02] pa mi počne tu moralizirati

760
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:46,800
[SPEAKER_02] u ljudskim pravima,

761
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:48,760
[SPEAKER_02] a da ne kažem ovi moralizatori,

762
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,619
[SPEAKER_02] kojih, znate na koga mislim,

763
00:38:50,619 --> 00:38:51,980
[SPEAKER_02] na ljevoj opciji,

764
00:38:52,059 --> 00:38:53,639
[SPEAKER_02] ili na filozofskom fakultetu,

765
00:38:53,639 --> 00:38:55,239
[SPEAKER_02] koji misle da su popili

766
00:38:55,239 --> 00:38:56,639
[SPEAKER_02] svu znanost svijeta.

767
00:38:56,639 --> 00:38:58,320
[SPEAKER_02] A u biti prave veliku,

768
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,199
[SPEAKER_02] veliku štetu,

769
00:38:59,199 --> 00:39:01,480
[SPEAKER_02] jer kontaminiraju naše studente

770
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:02,480
[SPEAKER_02] sa svojim stavom.

771
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] A kad ste spomenuli komunizam,

772
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] baš dobro da ste se toga dotakli,

773
00:39:06,019 --> 00:39:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] da nas ljudi ne bi svrstavali

774
00:39:08,420 --> 00:39:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] određene kutija,

775
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] i ne samo zbog toga,

776
00:39:10,199 --> 00:39:11,400
[SPEAKER_00] nego da zahvatimo sve.

777
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kako zdravo odgovoriti,

778
00:39:14,019 --> 00:39:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] zdravo kontrirati

779
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] ovome što sada govorimo,

780
00:39:18,119 --> 00:39:19,239
[SPEAKER_00] jer znamo da puno ljudi,

781
00:39:19,239 --> 00:39:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo na ovoj desnoj strani

782
00:39:20,940 --> 00:39:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] političkog spektra,

783
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] lako ode u proruske stavove,

784
00:39:25,019 --> 00:39:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] u potpuno druge kontre,

785
00:39:26,579 --> 00:39:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] koje isto znamo da nemaju smisla,

786
00:39:28,380 --> 00:39:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo iz naše hrvatske vizure.

787
00:39:30,599 --> 00:39:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako se zdravo hrvatski postavite,

788
00:39:33,099 --> 00:39:34,280
[SPEAKER_00] evo da tako kažem,

789
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] u tim utjecani.

790
00:39:35,599 --> 00:39:36,900
[SPEAKER_02] To opet imamo puno pitanja,

791
00:39:36,900 --> 00:39:38,460
[SPEAKER_02] mogu vam da svom primjeru reći.

792
00:39:38,460 --> 00:39:40,980
[SPEAKER_02] Čuli ste za gospodina Ličinu,

793
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:42,360
[SPEAKER_02] Đorđe Ličina,

794
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:43,840
[SPEAKER_02] on je bio udbaški novinar

795
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,500
[SPEAKER_02] za pisaj za vjesnik,

796
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:47,599
[SPEAKER_02] on je mene i Ante Nobilo,

797
00:39:47,599 --> 00:39:49,280
[SPEAKER_02] isto koji je tužio moj tato

798
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,940
[SPEAKER_02] i završio četiri godine u zatvori,

799
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:53,519
[SPEAKER_02] odbaški komunistički tužitelj.

800
00:39:53,519 --> 00:39:56,800
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam onda slovio u Jugoslaviji komunistički,

801
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:59,539
[SPEAKER_02] kad sam imao politički azil u Americi,

802
00:39:59,539 --> 00:40:02,039
[SPEAKER_02] da radim da sam cija špijun.

803
00:40:02,039 --> 00:40:03,880
[SPEAKER_02] A nedavno me indes...

804
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:05,059
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam čuo i ruski špijun.

805
00:40:05,059 --> 00:40:06,139
[SPEAKER_02] Da, a sada sam me provlastio,

806
00:40:06,139 --> 00:40:07,260
[SPEAKER_02] da sam ruski špijun,

807
00:40:07,260 --> 00:40:09,019
[SPEAKER_02] zbog toga što imam kakve take,

808
00:40:09,019 --> 00:40:10,000
[SPEAKER_02] već 30 godina,

809
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,559
[SPEAKER_02] ali nije stalno.

810
00:40:11,559 --> 00:40:13,380
[SPEAKER_02] Ali imam čitan knjige

811
00:40:13,380 --> 00:40:14,860
[SPEAKER_02] i nešto sam napisao

812
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:16,139
[SPEAKER_02] za gospodina Ana Dugina.

813
00:40:16,139 --> 00:40:18,800
[SPEAKER_02] I bio sam njegov gost

814
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:20,179
[SPEAKER_02] i više smo govorili

815
00:40:20,179 --> 00:40:21,079
[SPEAKER_02] o Dostojevskom,

816
00:40:21,079 --> 00:40:22,300
[SPEAKER_02] i o homo sovjetikusu,

817
00:40:22,300 --> 00:40:24,679
[SPEAKER_02] o psihopatologiji komunizma.

818
00:40:24,679 --> 00:40:26,280
[SPEAKER_02] On to jako dobro slača.

819
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:28,119
[SPEAKER_02] O Zinovjevu sam govorio,

820
00:40:28,119 --> 00:40:29,760
[SPEAKER_02] o Bukovskom i o disidentima.

821
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:31,820
[SPEAKER_02] Ali su me već neki,

822
00:40:31,820 --> 00:40:33,219
[SPEAKER_02] prvenstveno mislim Indijek,

823
00:40:33,219 --> 00:40:34,239
[SPEAKER_02] sve su me proglasili

824
00:40:34,239 --> 00:40:35,699
[SPEAKER_02] da sam ruski špijun.

825
00:40:35,980 --> 00:40:38,019
[SPEAKER_02] ja ne želim ničiji stav zaozimati,

826
00:40:38,019 --> 00:40:39,860
[SPEAKER_02] jer ne pripadam niti jedne stranci,

827
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:41,219
[SPEAKER_02] niti jedne sekti

828
00:40:41,219 --> 00:40:42,940
[SPEAKER_02] i bit ću isto tako kritičan

829
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:44,800
[SPEAKER_02] ako treba prema katoličkom kleru

830
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,860
[SPEAKER_02] i biskupskoj konferenciji u Americi.

831
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:48,460
[SPEAKER_02] Vrlo kritičan sam prema njima,

832
00:40:48,460 --> 00:40:50,360
[SPEAKER_02] kao što ću biti kritičan

833
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:52,679
[SPEAKER_02] i prema palo-komunistima

834
00:40:52,679 --> 00:40:54,900
[SPEAKER_02] koji dobivaju iz državnog proačuna,

835
00:40:54,900 --> 00:40:55,639
[SPEAKER_02] ili raznorazni,

836
00:40:55,639 --> 00:40:57,019
[SPEAKER_02] da ih na sad ne spominjem imena,

837
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:58,860
[SPEAKER_02] raznoraznim NGO-ovcima,

838
00:40:58,860 --> 00:41:01,719
[SPEAKER_02] ne vladenim institucijima

839
00:41:01,719 --> 00:41:03,900
[SPEAKER_02] koje primaju vaše nosima i moja novca.

840
00:41:03,900 --> 00:41:06,579
[SPEAKER_02] Da, znači...

841
00:41:06,579 --> 00:41:07,320
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam se ne znam

842
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:10,760
[SPEAKER_02] da li sam odgovorio na vaše pitanje.

843
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:11,659
[SPEAKER_02] Mi je slobodno možete...

844
00:41:11,659 --> 00:41:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] Pa znači, pretpostavljam,

845
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:15,260
[SPEAKER_00] i tu je teško dat neki uniformni odgovor

846
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se kao Hrvat postaviti

847
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče tih učecaja kapitalištkih,

848
00:41:19,699 --> 00:41:20,280
[SPEAKER_00] komunističkih,

849
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,639
[SPEAKER_00] jer znamo da nas sad u Hrvatskoj

850
00:41:21,639 --> 00:41:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] kapitalizam jede možda i više

851
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] nego što nas je na momente.

852
00:41:24,579 --> 00:41:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] Komunizam jeo.

853
00:41:25,800 --> 00:41:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to, tu upravo...

854
00:41:26,619 --> 00:41:27,780
[SPEAKER_00] Gubi se Hrvatski duh,

855
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] gubi se Hrvatski narod.

856
00:41:29,179 --> 00:41:31,260
[SPEAKER_02] Apsolutno, ja sam najlašao je sad.

857
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:32,900
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, tu ću jedan opet,

858
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:34,820
[SPEAKER_02] jedan metodološki,

859
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:36,199
[SPEAKER_02] jedan stav moje dati,

860
00:41:36,199 --> 00:41:37,460
[SPEAKER_02] čak mojim dobrim kolegama

861
00:41:37,460 --> 00:41:38,219
[SPEAKER_02] i prijateljima.

862
00:41:38,219 --> 00:41:39,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ima krasnih ljudi,

863
00:41:39,460 --> 00:41:41,800
[SPEAKER_02] ima ljudi koji lijepo znaju pisati za narod,

864
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:44,179
[SPEAKER_02] ima lijepih ljudi koji znaju pisati

865
00:41:44,179 --> 00:41:45,260
[SPEAKER_02] dobre podcaste,

866
00:41:45,260 --> 00:41:46,420
[SPEAKER_02] i dobre komentare.

867
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:48,840
[SPEAKER_02] Ima i finih studenta

868
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,059
[SPEAKER_02] koji bi nešto tijeli naučiti,

869
00:41:50,059 --> 00:41:51,420
[SPEAKER_02] prema da ja općenito

870
00:41:51,420 --> 00:41:53,280
[SPEAKER_02] dosta sam kritičan,

871
00:41:53,699 --> 00:41:56,360
[SPEAKER_02] prema našim profesorima,

872
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:59,300
[SPEAKER_02] čak i koji su dobrimi,

873
00:41:59,300 --> 00:42:01,420
[SPEAKER_02] koji imaju dobre silobose.

874
00:42:01,420 --> 00:42:03,079
[SPEAKER_02] Što sam htio reći?

875
00:42:03,079 --> 00:42:07,139
[SPEAKER_02] Najlakše je udarati po komunizmu

876
00:42:07,139 --> 00:42:09,199
[SPEAKER_02] i 24 sata govoriti

877
00:42:09,199 --> 00:42:11,340
[SPEAKER_02] o macelju, o teznoj,

878
00:42:11,340 --> 00:42:12,840
[SPEAKER_02] o lokacijama,

879
00:42:12,840 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_02] o poljima smrti,

